Since the first distribution of "ledit", a bug has been signaled and it
is now fixed. If your "ledit" has this problem, please take the last
version:
	ftp://ftp.inria.fr/lang/chamau/ledit.tar.gz

The bug is the following: if you paste a text with a lot of
parentheses, it is very slow, for "ledit" wait one second for each
closing parenthesis, the time to show the matching opening
parenthesis. In the last version, the bug is fixed and the "paste" is
immediate.

Thank you.

